{
  "stem": "964.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's Russia already.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's how we found out, we got-- they took us all the way into [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then later on, after a while, we got back into the truck and they went all the way to Vinnitsa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Vinnitsa, there was already part of this-- these people-- part of the German company which prepared for us, for them, the quarters.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In there, we worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had garages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was an abandoned post office, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had the base for trucks and all these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there we worked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We worked the whole winter-- fixed trucks, cleaned them, and welding, all this kind of-- all these kind of things-- the dirty work, nothing washing the-- if you took out a motor from the truck, we washed it with the petrol so they can work on it.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there we worked with them till-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] till spring, 1941-- no, spring 1941, right.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that time, the front already passed Kiev.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Germans took Kiev and advanced to Kiev.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the whole thing got folded up again, the whole operation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they moved-- and they moved to Kiev-- not really into the town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They moved in-- in Sviatoshino.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is before Kiev, 10 kilometers before Kiev.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they-- they settled down in a school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And for us, they gave us a few like shacks, little houses that we settled there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And interesting part is, when we were in-- in-- in-- in Vinnitsa, we tried to get in contact with-- we found out that when they're fixing the railroad, the trains-- not the railroad, the-- in the city, they're riding around in the-- the-- tram, [NON-ENGLISH] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the passenger cars, but were going by rail.",
      "word_count": 57
    }
  ],
